extendedInfo.description: After a lot of request I've made a version of my GO SMS iPhone (iOS) Theme with the new light blue bubbles!Hope you like it and thanks for the great support.Try it and rate it if you like it (5 stars make me happy! :P)If you have any problems, write me an email, I'll answer to you as quick as possible. Follow Me on Twitter http://bit.ly/Q0cPDk for the last news and updates. You can also write me there for support.**IMPORTANT** => there is an issue with jelly bean phone and go sms pro themes. The Play store can't correctly install the theme and you see a black background. Write me an e-mail, I can fix that if you contact me. PLEASE STOP ASKING FOR THE SENDING BAR AND THE ANIMATION:I'm sorry but for now go sms pro doesn't allow those modification to the animations, so I really can't add the sending bar and the sending animation of the bubble for now. If and when they will add those features I will immediately update the theme.Thank you**Disclaimer**:The word iPhone is used here to describe a graphic style. I don't own the trademark on that word and I'm not affiliated in any way with it's owners. This is only a GO SMS Pro theme that mimics the sms interface of the most famous phone in the world.***Remember***: this is a GO SMS Pro theme, so you need GO SMS Pro installed on your phone (it's free). Then you can select the theme called "iPhone Messages Theme" from the GO SMS Pro Theme settings, it will be the last theme down on the list.If you want the support for the Iphone emoji you simply need to install the GO SMS emoji plugin (it's free).
